text: Ferry Corsten, also known as System F, (born 4 December 1973) is a Dutch musical artist. He creates music in the electronica and trance varieties. He lives in Rotterdam, Netherlands. Ferry hosts his own radio show, "Corsten's Countdown". In 2009 Corsten ranked #7 on DJ Magazine's annual Top 100 DJ Poll. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch DJs Category:Entertainers from Rotterdam Category:Trance music
